§<~>17<~>.<~>In<~>the<~>first<~>book<~>we<~>considered<~>the<~>idea<~>merely<~>as<~>such<~>,<~>that<~>is<~>,<~>*NL*<~>only<~>according<~>to<~>its<~>general<~>form<~>.<~>It<~>is<~>true<~>that<~>as<~>far<~>as<~>the<~>abstract<~>*NL*<~>idea<~>,<~>the<~>concept<~>,<~>is<~>concerned<~>,<~>we<~>obtained<~>a<~>knowledge<~>of<~>it<~>in<~>respect<~>*NL*<~>of<~>its<~>content<~>also<~>,<~>because<~>it<~>has<~>content<~>and<~>meaning<~>only<~>in<~>relation<~>*NL*<~>to<~>the<~>idea<~>of<~>perception<~>,<~>without<~>which<~>it<~>would<~>be<~>worthless<~>and<~>empty<~>.<~>*NL*<~>Accordingly<~>,<~>directing<~>our<~>attention<~>exclusively<~>to<~>the<~>idea<~>of<~>*NL*<~>perception<~>,<~>we<~>shall<~>now<~>endeavour<~>to<~>arrive<~>at<~>a<~>knowledge<~>of<~>its<~>*NL*<~>content<~>,<~>its<~>more<~>exact<~>definition<~>,<~>and<~>the<~>forms<~>which<~>it<~>presents<~>to<~>us<~>.<~>*NL*<~>And<~>it<~>will<~>specially<~>interest<~>us<~>to<~>find<~>an<~>explanation<~>of<~>its<~>peculiar<~>*NL*<~>significance<~>,<~>that<~>significance<~>which<~>is<~>otherwise<~>merely<~>felt<~>,<~>but<~>on<~>*NL*<~>account<~>of<~>which<~>it<~>is<~>that<~>these<~>pictures<~>do<~>not<~>pass<~>by<~>us<~>entirely<~>*NL*<~>strange<~>and<~>meaningless<~>,<~>as<~>they<~>must<~>otherwise<~>do<~>,<~>but<~>speak<~>to<~>us<~>*NL*<~>directly<~>,<~>are<~>understood<~>,<~>and<~>obtain<~>an<~>interest<~>which<~>concerns<~>our<~>whole<~>*NL*<~>nature<~>.<~>*NL*<~>*NL*<~>We<~>direct<~>our<~>attention<~>to<~>mathematics<~>,<~>natural<~>science<~>,<~>and<~>philosophy<~>,<~>*NL*<~>for<~>each<~>of<~>these<~>holds<~>out<~>the<~>hope<~>that<~>it<~>will<~>afford<~>us<~>a<~>part<~>of<~>the<~>*NL*<~>explanation<~>we<~>desire<~>.<~>Now<~>,<~>taking<~>philosophy<~>first<~>,<~>we<~>find<~>that<~>it<~>is<~>*NL*<~>like<~>a<~>monster<~>with<~>many<~>heads<~>,<~>each<~>of<~>which<~>speaks<~>a<~>different<~>language<~>.<~>*NL*<~>They<~>are<~>not<~>,<~>indeed<~>,<~>all<~>at<~>variance<~>on<~>the<~>point<~>we<~>are<~>here<~>*NL*<~>considering<~>,<~>the<~>significance<~>of<~>the<~>idea<~>of<~>perception<~>.<~>For<~>,<~>with<~>the<~>*NL*<~>exception<~>of<~>the<~>Sceptics<~>and<~>the<~>Idealists<~>,<~>the<~>others<~>,<~>for<~>the<~>most<~>*NL*<~>part<~>,<~>speak<~>very<~>much<~>in<~>the<~>same<~>way<~>of<~>an<~>object<~>which<~>constitutes<~>the<~>*NL*<~>basis<~>of<~>the<~>idea<~>,<~>and<~>which<~>is<~>indeed<~>different<~>in<~>its<~>whole<~>being<~>and<~>*NL*<~>nature<~>from<~>the<~>idea<~>,<~>but<~>yet<~>is<~>in<~>all<~>points<~>as<~>like<~>it<~>as<~>one<~>egg<~>is<~>to<~>*NL*<~>another<~>.<~>But<~>this<~>does<~>not<~>help<~>us<~>,<~>for<~>we<~>are<~>quite<~>unable<~>to<~>distinguish<~>*NL*<~>such<~>an<~>object<~>from<~>the<~>idea<~>;<~>we<~>find<~>that<~>they<~>are<~>one<~>and<~>the<~>same<~>;<~>for<~>*NL*<~>every<~>object<~>always<~>and<~>for<~>ever<~>presupposes<~>a<~>subject<~>,<~>and<~>therefore<~>*NL*<~>remains<~>idea<~>,<~>so<~>that<~>we<~>recognised<~>objectivity<~>as<~>belonging<~>to<~>the<~>most<~>*NL*<~>universal<~>form<~>of<~>the<~>idea<~>,<~>which<~>is<~>the<~>division<~>into<~>subject<~>and<~>object<~>.<~>*NL*<~>Further<~>,<~>the<~>principle<~>of<~>sufficient<~>reason<~>,<~>which<~>is<~>referred<~>to<~>in<~>*NL*<~>support<~>of<~>this<~>doctrine<~>,<~>is<~>for<~>us<~>merely<~>the<~>form<~>of<~>the<~>idea<~>,<~>the<~>*NL*<~>orderly<~>combination<~>of<~>one<~>idea<~>with<~>another<~>,<~>but<~>not<~>the<~>combination<~>of<~>*NL*<~>the<~>whole<~>finite<~>or<~>infinite<~>series<~>of<~>ideas<~>with<~>something<~>which<~>is<~>not<~>*NL*<~>idea<~>at<~>all<~>,<~>and<~>which<~>can<~>not<~>therefore<~>be<~>presented<~>in<~>perception<~>.<~>Of<~>the<~>*NL*<~>Sceptics<~>and<~>Idealists<~>we<~>spoke<~>above<~>,<~>in<~>examining<~>the<~>controversy<~>about<~>*NL*<~>the<~>reality<~>of<~>the<~>outer<~>world<~>.<~>*NL*<~>*NL*<~>If<~>we<~>turn<~>to<~>mathematics<~>to<~>look<~>for<~>the<~>fuller<~>knowledge<~>we<~>desire<~>of<~>*NL*<~>the<~>idea<~>of<~>perception<~>,<~>which<~>we<~>have<~>,<~>as<~>yet<~>,<~>onl