with<~>them<~>,<~>is<~>precisely<~>that<~>in<~>which<~>the<~>*NL*<~>thing<~>manifested<~>,<~>the<~>thing-in-itself<~>,<~>directly<~>reveals<~>itself<~>.<~>It<~>follows<~>*NL*<~>from<~>this<~>that<~>the<~>most<~>complete<~>capacity<~>for<~>being<~>known<~>,<~>that<~>is<~>to<~>say<~>,<~>*NL*<~>the<~>greatest<~>clearness<~>,<~>distinctness<~>,<~>and<~>susceptibility<~>of<~>exhaustive<~>*NL*<~>explanation<~>,<~>will<~>necessarily<~>belong<~>to<~>that<~>which<~>pertains<~>to<~>knowledge<~>*NL*<~>as<~>such<~>,<~>and<~>thus<~>to<~>the<~>form<~>of<~>knowledge<~>;<~>but<~>not<~>to<~>that<~>which<~>in<~>*NL*<~>itself<~>is<~>not<~>idea<~>,<~>not<~>object<~>,<~>but<~>which<~>has<~>become<~>knowledge<~>only<~>*NL*<~>through<~>entering<~>these<~>forms<~>;<~>in<~>other<~>words<~>,<~>has<~>become<~>idea<~>,<~>object<~>.<~>*NL*<~>Thus<~>only<~>that<~>which<~>depends<~>entirely<~>upon<~>being<~>an<~>object<~>of<~>knowledge<~>,<~>*NL*<~>upon<~>existing<~>as<~>idea<~>in<~>general<~>and<~>as<~>such<~>-LRB-<~>not<~>upon<~>that<~>which<~>*NL*<~>becomes<~>known<~>,<~>and<~>has<~>only<~>become<~>idea<~>-RRB-<~>,<~>which<~>therefore<~>belongs<~>*NL*<~>without<~>distinction<~>to<~>everything<~>that<~>is<~>known<~>,<~>and<~>which<~>,<~>on<~>that<~>*NL*<~>account<~>,<~>is<~>found<~>just<~>as<~>well<~>if<~>we<~>start<~>from<~>the<~>subject<~>as<~>if<~>we<~>start<~>*NL*<~>from<~>the<~>object<~>,<~>--<~>this<~>alone<~>can<~>afford<~>us<~>without<~>reserve<~>a<~>sufficient<~>,<~>*NL*<~>exhaustive<~>knowledge<~>,<~>a<~>knowledge<~>which<~>is<~>clear<~>to<~>the<~>very<~>foundation<~>.<~>*NL*<~>But<~>this<~>consists<~>of<~>nothing<~>but<~>those<~>forms<~>of<~>all<~>phenomena<~>of<~>which<~>we<~>*NL*<~>are<~>conscious<~>a<~>priori<~>,<~>and<~>which<~>may<~>be<~>generally<~>expressed<~>as<~>the<~>*NL*<~>principle<~>of<~>sufficient<~>reason<~>.<~>Now<~>,<~>the<~>forms<~>of<~>this<~>principle<~>which<~>*NL*<~>occur<~>in<~>knowledge<~>of<~>perception<~>-LRB-<~>with<~>which<~>alone<~>we<~>are<~>here<~>conce