directly<~>*NL*<~>conditioned<~>by<~>time<~>and<~>space<~>,<~>into<~>which<~>the<~>will<~>itself<~>never<~>enters<~>.<~>*NL*<~>The<~>will<~>reveals<~>itself<~>as<~>completely<~>and<~>as<~>much<~>in<~>one<~>oak<~>as<~>in<~>*NL*<~>millions<~>.<~>Their<~>number<~>and<~>multiplication<~>in<~>space<~>and<~>time<~>has<~>no<~>meaning<~>*NL*<~>with<~>regard<~>to<~>it<~>,<~>but<~>only<~>with<~>regard<~>to<~>the<~>multiplicity<~>of<~>individuals<~>*NL*<~>who<~>know<~>in<~>space<~>and<~>time<~>,<~>and<~>who<~>are<~>themselves<~>multiplied<~>and<~>*NL*<~>dispersed<~>in<~>these<~>.<~>The<~>multiplicity<~>of<~>these<~>individuals<~>itself<~>belongs<~>*NL*<~>not<~>to<~>the<~>will<~>,<~>but<~>only<~>to<~>its<~>manifestation<~>.<~>We<~>may<~>therefore<~>say<~>that<~>*NL*<~>if<~>,<~>per<~>impossibile<~>,<~>a<~>single<~>real<~>existence<~>,<~>even<~>the<~>most<~>*NL*<~>insignificant<~>,<~>were<~>to<~>be<~>entirely<~>annihilated<~>,<~>the<~>whole<~>world<~>would<~>*NL*<~>necessarily<~>perish<~>with<~>it<~>.<~>The<~>great<~>mystic<~>Angelus<~>Silesius<~>feels<~>this<~>*NL*<~>when<~>he<~>says<~>--<~>*NL*<~>*NL*<~>*NL*<~>``<~>I<~>know<~>God<~>can<~>not<~>live<~>an<~>instant<~>without<~>me<~>,<~>*NL*<~>He<~>must<~>give<~>up<~>the<~>ghost<~>if<~>I<~>should<~>cease<~>to<~>be<~>.<~>''<~>*NL*<~>*NL*<~>*NL*<~>Men<~>have<~>tried<~>in<~>various<~>ways<~>to<~>bring<~>the<~>immeasurable<~>greatness<~>of<~>the<~>*NL*<~>material<~>universe<~>nearer<~>to<~>the<~>comprehension<~>of<~>us<~>all<~>,<~>and<~>then<~>they<~>*NL*<~>have<~>seized<~>the<~>opportunity<~>to<~>make<~>edifying<~>remarks<~>.<~>They<~>have<~>referred<~>*NL*<~>perhaps<~>to<~>the<~>relative<~>smallness<~>of<~>the<~>earth<~>,<~>and<~>indeed<~>of<~>man<~>;<~>or<~>,<~>on<~>*NL*<~>the<~>contrary<~>,<~>they<~>have<~>pointed<~>out<~>the<~>greatness<~>of<~>the<~>mind<~>of<~>this<~>man<~>*NL*<~>who<~>is<~>so<~>insignificant<~>--<~>the<~>mind<~>that<~>can<~>solve<~>,<~>comprehend<~>,<~>and<~>even<~>*NL*<~>measure<~>the<~>greatness<~>of<~>the<~>