a<~>qualitas<~>occulta<~>.<~>*NL*<~>*NL*<~>In<~>the<~>higher<~>grades<~>of<~>the<~>objectivity<~>of<~>will<~>we<~>see<~>individuality<~>*NL*<~>occupy<~>a<~>prominent<~>position<~>,<~>especially<~>in<~>the<~>case<~>of<~>man<~>,<~>where<~>it<~>*NL*<~>appears<~>as<~>the<~>great<~>difference<~>of<~>individual<~>characters<~>,<~>i.e.<~>,<~>as<~>*NL*<~>complete<~>personality<~>,<~>outwardly<~>expressed<~>in<~>strongly<~>marked<~>individual<~>*NL*<~>physiognomy<~>,<~>which<~>influences<~>the<~>whole<~>bodily<~>form<~>.<~>None<~>of<~>the<~>brutes<~>*NL*<~>have<~>this<~>individuality<~>in<~>anything<~>like<~>so<~>high<~>a<~>degree<~>,<~>though<~>the<~>*NL*<~>higher<~>species<~>of<~>them<~>have<~>a<~>trace<~>of<~>it<~>;<~>but<~>the<~>character<~>of<~>the<~>*NL*<~>species<~>completely<~>predominates<~>over<~>it<~>,<~>and<~>therefore<~>they<~>have<~>little<~>*NL*<~>individual<~>physiognomy<~>.<~>The<~>farther<~>down<~>we<~>go<~>,<~>the<~>more<~>completely<~>is<~>*NL*<~>every<~>trace<~>of<~>the<~>individual<~>character<~>lost<~>in<~>the<~>common<~>character<~>of<~>*NL*<~>the<~>species<~>,<~>and<~>the<~>physiognomy<~>of<~>the<~>species<~>alone<~>remains<~>.<~>We<~>know<~>the<~>*NL*<~>physiological<~>character<~>of<~>the<~>species<~>,<~>and<~>from<~>that<~>we<~>know<~>exactly<~>what<~>*NL*<~>is<~>to<~>be<~>expected<~>from<~>the<~>individual<~>;<~>while<~>,<~>on<~>the<~>contrary<~>,<~>in<~>the<~>*NL*<~>human<~>species<~>every<~>individual<~>has<~>to<~>be<~>studied<~>and<~>fathomed<~>for<~>himself<~>,<~>*NL*<~>which<~>,<~>if<~>we<~>wish<~>to<~>forecast<~>his<~>action<~>with<~>some<~>degree<~>of<~>certainty<~>,<~>*NL*<~>is<~>,<~>on<~>account<~>of<~>the<~>possibility<~>of<~>concealment<~>that<~>first<~>appears<~>with<~>*NL*<~>reason<~>,<~>a<~>matter<~>of<~>the<~>greatest<~>difficulty<~>.<~>It<~>is<~>probably<~>connected<~>with<~>*NL*<~>this<~>difference<~>of<~>the<~>human<~>species<~>from<~>all<~>others<~>,<~>that<~>the<~>folds<~>and<~>*NL*<~>convolutions<~>of<~>the<~>brain<~>,<~>whic