defines<~>,<~>enumerates<~>,<~>and<~>distinguishes<~>these<~>forces<~>,<~>and<~>then<~>*NL*<~>indicates<~>all<~>the<~>different<~>effects<~>in<~>which<~>each<~>force<~>appears<~>,<~>regulated<~>*NL*<~>by<~>the<~>difference<~>of<~>the<~>circumstances<~>,<~>always<~>in<~>accordance<~>with<~>its<~>own<~>*NL*<~>peculiar<~>character<~>,<~>which<~>it<~>discloses<~>in<~>obedience<~>to<~>an<~>invariable<~>rule<~>,<~>*NL*<~>called<~>a<~>law<~>of<~>nature<~>.<~>When<~>all<~>this<~>has<~>been<~>thoroughly<~>accomplished<~>*NL*<~>by<~>physics<~>in<~>every<~>particular<~>,<~>it<~>will<~>be<~>complete<~>,<~>and<~>its<~>work<~>will<~>be<~>*NL*<~>done<~>.<~>There<~>will<~>then<~>remain<~>no<~>unknown<~>force<~>in<~>unorganised<~>nature<~>,<~>nor<~>*NL*<~>any<~>effect<~>,<~>which<~>has<~>not<~>been<~>proved<~>to<~>be<~>the<~>manifestation<~>of<~>one<~>of<~>*NL*<~>these<~>forces<~>under<~>definite<~>circumstances<~>,<~>in<~>accordance<~>with<~>a<~>law<~>of<~>*NL*<~>nature<~>.<~>Yet<~>a<~>law<~>of<~>nature<~>remains<~>merely<~>the<~>observed<~>rule<~>according<~>to<~>*NL*<~>which<~>nature<~>invariably<~>proceeds<~>whenever<~>certain<~>definite<~>circumstances<~>*NL*<~>occur<~>.<~>Therefore<~>a<~>law<~>of<~>nature<~>may<~>be<~>defined<~>as<~>a<~>fact<~>expressed<~>*NL*<~>generally<~>--<~>un<~>fait<~>généralisé<~>--<~>and<~>thus<~>a<~>complete<~>enumeration<~>of<~>all<~>the<~>*NL*<~>laws<~>of<~>nature<~>would<~>only<~>be<~>a<~>complete<~>register<~>of<~>facts<~>.<~>The<~>*NL*<~>consideration<~>of<~>nature<~>as<~>a<~>whole<~>is<~>thus<~>completed<~>in<~>morphology<~>,<~>*NL*<~>which<~>enumerates<~>,<~>compares<~>,<~>and<~>arranges<~>all<~>the<~>enduring<~>forms<~>of<~>*NL*<~>organised<~>nature<~>.<~>Of<~>the<~>causes<~>of<~>the<~>appearance<~>of<~>the<~>individual<~>*NL*<~>creature<~>it<~>has<~>little<~>to<~>say<~>,<~>for<~>in<~>all<~>cases<~>this<~>is<~>procreation<~>-LRB-<~>the<~>*NL*<~>theory<~>of<~>which<~>is<~>a<~>separate<~>matter<~>-RRB-<~>,<~>and<~>in<~>rare<~>cases<~>the<~>gener