<~>most<~>terrible<~>distinctness<~>this<~>conflict<~>,<~>this<~>variance<~>with<~>itself<~>of<~>the<~>*NL*<~>will<~>,<~>and<~>we<~>find<~>homo<~>homini<~>lupus<~>.<~>Meanwhile<~>we<~>can<~>recognise<~>this<~>*NL*<~>strife<~>,<~>this<~>subjugation<~>,<~>just<~>as<~>well<~>in<~>the<~>lower<~>grades<~>of<~>the<~>*NL*<~>objectification<~>of<~>will<~>.<~>Many<~>insects<~>-LRB-<~>especially<~>ichneumon-flies<~>-RRB-<~>lay<~>*NL*<~>their<~>eggs<~>on<~>the<~>skin<~>,<~>and<~>even<~>in<~>the<~>body<~>of<~>the<~>larvæ<~>of<~>other<~>*NL*<~>insects<~>,<~>whose<~>slow<~>destruction<~>is<~>the<~>first<~>work<~>of<~>the<~>newly<~>hatched<~>*NL*<~>brood<~>.<~>The<~>young<~>hydra<~>,<~>which<~>grows<~>like<~>a<~>bud<~>out<~>of<~>the<~>old<~>one<~>,<~>and<~>*NL*<~>afterwards<~>separates<~>itself<~>from<~>it<~>,<~>fights<~>while<~>it<~>is<~>still<~>joined<~>to<~>*NL*<~>the<~>old<~>one<~>for<~>the<~>prey<~>that<~>offers<~>itself<~>,<~>so<~>that<~>the<~>one<~>snatches<~>it<~>*NL*<~>out<~>of<~>the<~>mouth<~>of<~>the<~>other<~>-LRB-<~>Trembley<~>,<~>Polypod.<~>,<~>ii<~>.<~>p.<~>110<~>,<~>and<~>iii<~>.<~>p.<~>*NL*<~>165<~>-RRB-<~>.<~>But<~>the<~>bulldog-ant<~>of<~>Australia<~>affords<~>us<~>the<~>most<~>extraordinary<~>*NL*<~>example<~>of<~>this<~>kind<~>;<~>for<~>if<~>it<~>is<~>cut<~>in<~>two<~>,<~>a<~>battle<~>begins<~>between<~>the<~>*NL*<~>head<~>and<~>the<~>tail<~>.<~>The<~>head<~>seizes<~>the<~>tail<~>with<~>its<~>teeth<~>,<~>and<~>the<~>tail<~>*NL*<~>defends<~>itself<~>bravely<~>by<~>stinging<~>the<~>head<~>:<~>the<~>battle<~>may<~>last<~>for<~>half<~>*NL*<~>an<~>hour<~>,<~>until<~>they<~>die<~>or<~>are<~>dragged<~>away<~>by<~>other<~>ants<~>.<~>This<~>contest<~>*NL*<~>takes<~>place<~>every<~>time<~>the<~>experiment<~>is<~>tried<~>.<~>-LRB-<~>From<~>a<~>letter<~>by<~>Howitt<~>*NL*<~>in<~>the<~>W.<~>Journal<~>,<~>reprinted<~>in<~>Galignani<~>'s<~>Messenger<~>,<~>17th<~>November<~>*NL*<~>1855<~>.<~>-RRB-<~>On<~>the<~>banks<~>of<~>the<~>Missouri<~>one<~>sometimes<~>sees<~>a<~>mighty<